{"tid":1280820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢幾個禮拜令我最無力嘅唔係政府唔係黑警...","createTime":"2019-07-03T05:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:36:28.000Z","uid":26405,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0dff58441ca8dbc0120f97dc4f322ac8c4581647","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"係咁多位想以死相諫嘅義士呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府唔聽民意，我地可以繼續發夢抗爭<br />\n<br />\n黑警仆街，我地可以繼續搵方法追究到底<br />\n<br />\n但係如果你地以死相諫呢？我地可以點樣攞返你地條命返來？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你走咗，對邊個影響最大？係政府？黑警？係我地呢班<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同伴</span></span>呀！！！我地會擔心，會傷心，嗰種保護唔到你地嘅無力感比任何一切都令我地更加自責......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地堅持咗咁耐，為嘅係咩呀？係為咗我地自己，為咗我地咁多個香港人自己呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n少咗你，咁我地成功爭取返來又有咩意義？可以同邊個分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，你地條命，同我地爭取緊嘅嘢，係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一樣咁重要！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論以後結果係點，你仲有我地喺度！只要我地仲喺度，我地就會繼續去爭取，直至成功因為止！你地可以失望，可以傷心，但係唔可以絕望！因為我地仲未輸！我地要一齊贏，一齊睇到成功嘅嗰一日！！！"},{"pid":"351f023c4ff004f0bb8507c91f79db2c2ec5bc4d","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"如果你某一刻突然萌生起以死相諫嘅念頭，麻煩你睇一百次下面呢條片，聽清楚小妹妹講咗啲乜！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1248882771954821&amp;id=169166456593130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1248882771954821%26id%3D169166456593130&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsOxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=515cbce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1248882771954821&amp;id=169166456593130</a>"},{"pid":"08b08dfdd221bf99295d271e9e7b943304bdb61e","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:02:00.000Z","msg":"有啲乜嘢，可以搵身邊嘅人，或者搵我地傾，唔好自己決定完就算！"},{"pid":"9b8cc60f5b442f45836f8be616382a61b4cfc3f9","tid":1280820,"uid":199332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"推！仲要一齊贏㗎！"},{"pid":"3b24d4fdb90e236955a8410f03cde3ada1d7bfaa","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b8cc60f5b442f45836f8be616382a61b4cfc3f9","tid":1280820,"uid":199332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"推！仲要一齊贏㗎！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"無錯！"},{"pid":"5521b926d1acbe1a258342d757f434cb35e8462e","tid":1280820,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:35:33.000Z","msg":"認同，其他人欠債、供唔掂樓、生意失敗跳樓我無資格叫人唔好跳<br />\n但為香港咁死真係好唔值，始終仲有好多藍絲同賣港賊<br />\n有時都唔想為呢d人爭取，更何況死<br />\n<br />\n香港最後變成點，真係仲有好多同路人陪住你<br />\n200萬人上街又上過，立法會又衝過<br />\n最後都改變唔到嘅話<br />\n已經好過咩都唔做就被赤化<br />\n仲要依家雖然唔係贏，但亦未輸<br />\n絕d講，投白票都有用過已死相諫"},{"pid":"0699c7e9b3f9729992f4547928e2eb7803a0ee6f","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1859c7d5e38d5addb819ac7e5e2d0ed9a1b02a92","tid":1280820,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:48.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"033db61929bbd349f1a8fdd497da7baf1b711275","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"唔好再有下一個喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bddba3bf0ffce48601904e79bbec842e2e7edf","tid":1280820,"uid":144848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"一個都不能少<br />\n我哋要嘅係齊上齊落"},{"pid":"8ace7d338f9bae0173910d94c72f184db3caa611","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手推畀其他義士睇<br />\n真係一個都不能再少喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b299c917a84261d09888deb0c417ce4b432f9e","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:09:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0508a079f4136d1205332c21e0cb638a891db3a3","tid":1280820,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"推一推"}]}